These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: funk, rock, classical, gospel, hip-hop, techno
6 different pets are kept: hamster, fish, ferret, horse, rat, goat
 1. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 3. the fan of hip-hop is not the owner of the rat##6
 4. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 5. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 6. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
 7. the owner of the rat is not the fan of rock##6
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of funk is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the fan of gospel##7
10. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
12. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
13. the owner of the hamster is the fan of funk##1
14. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
15. the fan of techno is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | funk | classical   | techno     | rock    | hip-hop   |
| Pet           | rat | hamster   | goat | horse | ferret | fish |

