.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, romance, spy, scientific, mystery, thriller
6 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, cat, goat, lizard, bird
 1. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 7. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not the owner of the lizard##6
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the goat##7
11. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
12. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
14. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
15. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
16. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
17. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person watching mystery movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | thriller | scientific | mystery     | spy      | crime |
| Pet           | frog         | cat        | lizard   | goat | rabbit | bird    |

