.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, coffee, sprite, juice, milk
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: handball, tennis, golf, volleyball, badminton, soccer
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person drinking sprite##6
 5. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's sport is handball##6
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
10. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking almond-milk##7
11. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
13. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
14. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | juice        | sprite | milk    | fanta    | coffee | almond-milk |
| Sport      | tennis | badminton  | soccer | volleyball | handball | golf      |

