The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: time-travel, comedy, zombie, epic, musical, disaster
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is not the person drinking sprite##6
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking sprite##7
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking iced-tea##7
 8. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking juice##7
10. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
13. the person watching zombie movies is the person drinking juice##1
14. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | juice | cola | iced-tea | tea | sprite | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | epic      | time-travel | musical     | disaster | comedy |

