.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: writing, cooking, skydiving, woodworking, hiking, filmmaking
The people have 6 different jobs:  freelancer, musician, chef, analyst, writer, teacher
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the analyst and the musician##7
 5. the teacher is on the left or right of the chef##3
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the writer##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
 8. the writer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the writer is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
10. the musician is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
11. the teacher is on the right of the chef##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
13. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
14. the musician is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
15. the writer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | skydiving         | woodworking | cooking | writing   | filmmaking | hiking  |
| Job     | writer | analyst  | chef  | teacher | musician  | freelancer |

 